  {
    "type": "list",
    "sub_type": "text",
    "list_items": [
      "·Represent a molecule as a set of spheres per atom, regressa set of properties. ",
      "·One feature channel per atom type. ",
      "·Use directionalatributes only (no radius). "
    ],
    "bbox": [
